I got a crash stack on android, it pointed to method FontAtlasCache::purgeCachedData, but i can not create a test case to always create this bug. I checked the code , find the bug might cause by that:
In FontAtlasCache::purgeCachedData, 
    for (auto & atlas:_atlasMap)
    {
        atlas.second->purgeTexturesAtlas();
    }
It invoke FontAtlas::purgeTexturesAtlas, which invoke cclabel's purgeTextureListener, which call FontAtlasCache::releaseFontAtlas. FontAtlasCache::releaseFontAtlas change the _atlasMap. 

The loop process of _atlasMap might be affected in the process, and cause crash.
